---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
	title="Isaac McFadyen"
	description="Hi! I'm Isaac McFadyen, a Canadian Computer Science student and developer, and this is my site."
	header={false}
>
	<div class="max-w-screen-sm mx-auto my-24 flex flex-col px-4">
		<h1
			class="text-4xl font-bold"
			transition:name="site-title"
			transition:animate="none"
		>
			Isaac McFadyen
		</h1>
		<h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">
			Computer Science Student & Future Software Engineer
		</h2>

		<div class="flex mt-4 gap-4">
			<a
				href="https://github.com/isaac-mcfadyen"
				class="hover:brightness-75 transition"
			>
				<svg
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					width="36"
					height="36"
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					><path
						fill="currentColor"
						d="M12 2A10 10 0 0 0 2 12c0 4.42 2.87 8.17 6.84 9.5c.5.08.66-.23.66-.5v-1.69c-2.77.6-3.36-1.34-3.36-1.34c-.46-1.16-1.11-1.47-1.11-1.47c-.91-.62.07-.6.07-.6c1 .07 1.53 1.03 1.53 1.03c.87 1.52 2.34 1.07 2.91.83c.09-.65.35-1.09.63-1.34c-2.22-.25-4.55-1.11-4.55-4.92c0-1.11.38-2 1.03-2.71c-.1-.25-.45-1.29.1-2.64c0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.02c.79-.22 1.65-.33 2.5-.33c.85 0 1.71.11 2.5.33c1.91-1.29 2.75-1.02 2.75-1.02c.55 1.35.2 2.39.1 2.64c.65.71 1.03 1.6 1.03 2.71c0 3.82-2.34 4.66-4.57 4.91c.36.31.69.92.69 1.85V21c0 .27.16.59.67.5C19.14 20.16 22 16.42 22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2Z"
					></path></svg
				>
				<span class="sr-only">Github</span>
			</a>
			<a
				href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/isaac-mcfadyen-22012a259/"
				class="hover:brightness-75 transition"
			>
				<svg
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					width="36"
					height="36"
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					><path
						fill="currentColor"
						d="M19 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14m-.5 15.5v-5.3a3.26 3.26 0 0 0-3.26-3.26c-.85 0-1.84.52-2.32 1.3v-1.11h-2.79v8.37h2.79v-4.93c0-.77.62-1.4 1.39-1.4a1.4 1.4 0 0 1 1.4 1.4v4.93h2.79M6.88 8.56a1.68 1.68 0 0 0 1.68-1.68c0-.93-.75-1.69-1.68-1.69a1.69 1.69 0 0 0-1.69 1.69c0 .93.76 1.68 1.69 1.68m1.39 9.94v-8.37H5.5v8.37h2.77Z"
					></path></svg
				>
				<span class="sr-only">Linkedin</span>
			</a>
		</div>

		<p class="mt-6 mb-1 text-lg">
			Hey! My name is Isaac McFadyen. I'm a <svg
				xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
				width="20"
				height="20"
				viewBox="0 0 36 36"
				class="inline-block align-middle mx-1"
				><path
					fill="#D52B1E"
					d="M4 5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v18a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h6V5H4zm28 0h-6v26h6a4 4 0 0 0 4-4V9a4 4 0 0 0-4-4z"
				></path><path fill="#EEE" d="M10 5h16v26H10z"></path><path
					fill="#D52B1E"
					d="M18.615 22.113c1.198.139 2.272.264 3.469.401l-.305-1.002a.46.46 0 0 1 .159-.476l3.479-2.834l-.72-.339c-.317-.113-.23-.292-.115-.722l.531-1.936l-2.021.427c-.197.03-.328-.095-.358-.215l-.261-.911l-1.598 1.794c-.227.288-.687.288-.544-.376l.683-3.634l-.917.475c-.257.144-.514.168-.657-.089l-1.265-2.366v.059v-.059l-1.265 2.366c-.144.257-.401.233-.658.089l-.916-.475l.683 3.634c.144.664-.317.664-.544.376l-1.598-1.793l-.26.911c-.03.12-.162.245-.359.215l-2.021-.427l.531 1.936c.113.43.201.609-.116.722l-.72.339l3.479 2.834c.138.107.208.3.158.476l-.305 1.002l3.47-.401c.106 0 .176.059.175.181l-.214 3.704h.956l-.213-3.704c.002-.123.071-.182.177-.182z"
				></path></svg
			> Canadian Computer Science student at <a
				href="https://trentu.ca"
				class="font-bold text-green-500 hover:text-green-700 transition"
				rel="noopener"
				target="_blank">Trent University</a
			>, and have a passion for web development and backend applications.
		</p>
		<p class="my-1 text-lg">
			I'm a Community Champion on the <a
				href="https://discord.gg/cloudflaredev"
				class="font-bold text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-600 transition"
				rel="noopener"
				target="_blank">Cloudflare Developers Discord</a
			> and MVP on the <a
				href="https://community.cloudflare.com"
				class="font-bold text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-600 transition"
				rel="noopener"
				target="_blank">Cloudflare Community</a
			> forum. Feel free to join and say hi!
		</p>
		<p class="my-1 text-lg">
			You can also check out my <a href="/blog" class="font-bold link-blue"
				>blog</a
			>, where I post miscellaneous things about software and tech, as well as
			some of my <a href="/projects" class="link-blue">projects</a> and <a
				href="/as213339"
				class="link-blue">AS213339</a
			> that I run for educational purposes. <a
				href="/contact"
				class="link-blue">Reach out</a
			> if have any questions or want to chat!
		</p>
	</div>
</MainLayout>
